# Databricks â€“ Data Processing

## Overview
Databricks notebooks are used to transform data from Bronze to Silver and Gold layers using Delta Lake.

---

## Bronze
- CSV to Delta conversion
- Schema inference
- Partitioning by league

---

## Silver
- Data cleansing
- Type casting
- Data standardization

---

## Gold
- Fact and dimension modeling
- Analytical tables
- Optimized for Power BI consumption

---

## Best Practices Applied
- Delta Lake ACID compliance
- Idempotent writes
- Modular notebooks
